00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
But what's available for free is if you want to get a feel of the core strategy

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
how we're trying to teach this and how we teach this in real life,

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.000
you could go to steveblank.com category/Lean LaunchPad or just click on the link.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:41.000
